original: Öhlin, Ernst Wilhelm, kyrkoherde. Blidsberg, f. 13/1/91 i Sthlm. G. 1. m. Dagny Kjällgren; 2. m. Stina Forssell. Barn: Klas Anders f. 28. — Stud:ex. i Upps. 18, teol. fil. ex. 20, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv. f. Skara stift 23. Tjg. s. v. kommin. i Od, Ulricehamn, v. pastor i Fägre samt pas-torsadj. o. kommin. i Ulricehamn, kyrkoih. i Blidsberg sed. 33. Ordf. i kyrkostämmior m. m.
translated: Öhlin, Ernst Wilhelm, clergyman. Born on 13/1/91 in Stockholm. Married 1st to Dagny Kjällgren; 2nd to Stina Forssell. Children: Klas Anders born on 28. — Completed upper secondary school in Uppsala in 1918, theological philosophy degree in 1920, theological candidate, practical theological examination, and ordained as a priest in Skara Diocese in 1923. Served as a curate in Od, Ulricehamn, assistant vicar in Fägre, as well as assistant vicar and curate in Ulricehamn, and became a parish priest in Blidsberg in 1933. Chairman of church assemblies, etc.
